xbrli:xbrl.in-capmkt:DetailsOfProjectRelatedToReduc:
The Company has implemented and following few of the initiatives to reduce Green House Gas emission:
•	Adoption of Renewable energy through solar; 
•	Replacement of old conventional lights with LED's;
•	Installation of energy efficient air compressor; and
•	Replacement of old motors with premium efficiency IE3 motors
